This module adds the measure "Volume Delivered" in the sale report view.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

#. Go to *Sales > Reporting > Sales*.
#. Add the "Volume Delivered" measure from your "Measures" dropdown in your analysis.
